{"tid":1506843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒]黨鐵要同TVB同一下場！！！","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T05:11:50.000Z","uid":263622,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef26049847ef72041b44a529e63f1bc0c450d600","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"相信大家對黨鐵停站打壓遊行<br />\n同運狗都好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋絕對唔可以放過呢嚿廢鐵！</span></span><br />\n有人提過玩跳閘，但係未必個個做到<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span></span>一定個個都得<br />\n<br />\n本地客運只係佔黨鐵四成收益<br />\n而<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">廣告費同租金係佔五成</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">港鐵車站同商場舖頭</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">喺黨鐵落廣告嘅客戶</span></span><br />\n絕對係黨鐵<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">春袋</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">將黨鐵成為另一個TVB！</span></span>"},{"pid":"718af8ae5addafc15660bd45a48f4efb316c8133","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:19.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%B1%AC%E6%96%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258A%25B5%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%2596%25BC%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%2F&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=25e5e0b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258A%25B5%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%2596%25BC%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%2F&h=f402d69b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E5%B1%AC%E6%96%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5/</a>"},{"pid":"8d81ae26f27d2adb6b269d76e92d7b29aa5d8bc1","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"//原來本地客運業務只佔港鐵經營利潤不足四成，車站商務和物業租貸業務去年合共錄得約 100 億元收益，佔經營利潤接近五成，這才是港鐵收益的最主要來源。大家不要忘記，港鐵另外一個身份，就是香港其中一個最大的地產霸權。//"},{"pid":"fdfd09c19648e64568b3344cd625210a2cf58e31","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:33:42.000Z","msg":"//車站商務是指各港鐵車站内的商舖租金和廣告牌收入。物業租貸是指港鐵旗下 13 個商場和停車場，包括<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圓方、奧海城一期、九龍灣德福廣場、青衣城、將軍澳 PopCorn、杏花新城、荃灣綠楊坊、坑口連理街、沙田 Citylink、火炭駿景廣場、屯門海趣坊、新屯門廣場、屯門恆福商場</span></span>。未來項目包括<span style=\"color: red;\">將軍澳日出康城商場、大圍商場和黃竹坑商場</span>。拒絕到以上地點消費，罷買租用港鐵站内廣告牌的商戶，大家都應該做得到。//"},{"pid":"e3df2112581385727d3b9c330d54e4331fb14866","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"自推十連！"},{"pid":"64a7b8340d04ca3ec92c6535c0b1ad1e351d0dae","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"6f297e261e4c64c286e9879069fe5a875d2f4130","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:34:41.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"e08fd3b0716997fd98b4fd58082687e29bc4ccd0","tid":1506843,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:34:54.000Z","msg":"八"}